{
  "texts": [
    "The micro F1 score -a weighted mean of category-specific F1 scores -was used for relation extraction and document classification.",
    "Pearson correlation coefficients were calculated to evaluate performance on the sentence similarity task.",
    "For the question answering tasks, accuracy -the overall proportion of correct answers -was used.",
    "All analyses were performed using Python (3.9) packages, with scikit-learn (1.4.0) and scipy (1.12.0) for computing the metrics.",
    "The version of GPT models used was gpt-35-turbo, 0613 and gpt-4, 0613."
  ]
}